<L>__{interior mausoleum same time}
<A>__{inside it is catacomb like, filled with the bleached bones of the addams dead. gomez's torch casts shadows one of which belongs to wednesday, curled asleep on a stone sarcophagus. relieved to find her, gomez approaches quietly. he doesn't want to wake her up. he lifts her tenderly in his arms.}
